               <msContents>
                  <summary>Prayer of Saint Peter, ጸሎተ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡, arranged for the days of the week</summary>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="76r"/>
                    <title>Prayer of Saint Peter, ጸሎተ፡ ጴጥሮስ።‎</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      ‎በስመ፡ ወወልድ፡ ጸሎቱ፡ ለጴጥሮስ፡ ዝንቱ፡ ውእቱ፡ ዘየዓቢ፡ ‎‎እምሐዋርያቲሁ፡ ወዘኃረዮ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ወልደ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ሕያው፡ ‎‎እምቅድመ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ ሐዋርያቲሁ፡ ወጸውዖሙ፡ ለኵሎሙ፡ ሐዋርያቲሁ፡ ‎‎ወነበረ፡ ምስሌሆሙ፡ ወባረኮሙ <gap reason="omitted"/>‎
                    </incipit>
                    <note>arranged for the days of the week: Monday (<locus target="#1r"/>), Tuesday (<locus target="#11v"/>), ‎Wednesday (<locus target="#22r"/>), Thursday (<locus target="#38v"/>), Friday (<locus target="#51v"/>), Saturday (<locus target="#59r"/>), ‎Sunday (<locus target="#66r"/>), Daily (<locus target="#72r"/>)‎</note>
                  </msItem>
